subSubSection.paragraph:
Abdomen
(
Fig. 3B, C
): Tergite 6 bare. Sternite 1 setulose, with long setulae marginally. Sternite 5 (
Fig. 6A
) processes with long lateral setae on the outer margin and shorter setae on the inner margin.

